# Form UI Rules

## Layout

- Use sections (cards):

  1. Basic Info
  2. Content
  3. Media
  4. SEO
  5. Settings

---

## Grid

- Use 2-column layout
- Content editor full width

---

## Inputs
- alway add label with localization. Example "label="@L["Icon"].Value"  (if not exits please add new to /services/{currentservice}/*.KHHub.{currentservice}.Contracts/Localization/*/en.json and any localization file .json )

- Title → text
- Slug → auto generate
- Category → select
- Tags → multi select (typeahead)
- Thumbnail → upload and preview image 
- Content → rich text (TinyMceEditor) editor with upload image and can show image in content 

---

## UX

- Show validation inline
- Save button top-right
- Cancel button secondary

---

## Actions

Top right:
- Delete if is edit page
- Save (if is create page)/ Edit (if is edit page) 
- Save And Publish (or active) if dto contain status enum 
- Back to list
